<section>
  <div class="mb-4">
    <h2 class="h4">Ranking</h2>
    <p>
      Welcome to the XLPSR Challenge ranking page! Here, you can find the latest
      updates on the performance of submissions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header fw-semibold">Top 10 Ranking</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="table-responsive">
        <table class="table table-striped table-hover align-middle">
          <thead class="table-dark">
            <tr>
              <th scope="col">Ranking</th>
              <th scope="col">Team</th>
              <th scope="col">mAP@50</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <% topTeams.forEach((team, index) => { %>
              <tr>
                <td><span class="badge bg-primary"><%= index + 1 %><%= ['st','nd','rd'][index] || 'th' %></span></td>
                <td>
                  <%= index === 0 ? ' ðŸ†' : index === 1 ? ' ðŸ¥ˆ' : '' %>
                  <%= team.teamName.trim() %>
                  <%= index === 0 ? ' ðŸ†' : index === 1 ? ' ðŸ¥ˆ' : '' %>
                </td>
                <td><%= (team.score * 100).toFixed(2) %></td>
              </tr>
            <% }) %>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header fw-semibold">Upload Your Results</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="mb-2">
        Upload a JSON file containing your model's outputs for XLPSR.
        You will be prompted for your registration password.
      </p>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" disabled>
        Upload Results
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-3">
    <h2 class="h4">Evaluation & Ranking Notes</h2>
    <p>
      Automated screening uses an external OCR engine to compute Character Error Rate (CER), alongside a Visual Quality Metric (VQM) such as BRISQUE/NIQE/MUSIQ.
      A combined score <code>S = Î±Â·CER + Î²Â·VQM</code> ranks submissions for Stage 1. Final winners are selected via expert evaluation (Stage 2).
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header fw-semibold">Leaderboard Notes</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="mb-0">Live ranking aggregates the current combined score per team. Detailed per-sequence metrics and CER/VQM breakdowns will be displayed after evaluation periods.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
